              "speaker": "E T E R N A L   P E T I T I O N E R",
              "text": "Find the S T A M P at the old Shrine. Without it, you are just a person standing in fog. With it, you are a person standing in fog who may P R O C E E D."
            },
            {
              "speaker": "E T E R N A L   P E T I T I O N E R",
              "text": "I have been waiting so long that my legs became roots. But my number will be called. I B E L I E V E."
